    "updated_at": "2015-07-20T09:12:00Z",
    "body": "Chrome browser doesn't seems to handle it, so if you think it should you can create an issue in Chromium project.\n\nI reproduced by:\n1. Open Chrome 43\n2. Open Google and open devtools\n3. Run `document.addEventListener('keypress', function(e) {\n   console.log('keypress', e);\n   });` in devtools\n4. Press `ESC` and there is no output\n"
