    "created_at": "2015-07-20T19:14:34Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-07-20T19:15:07Z",
    "body": "Afaik, `keypress` only captures key events that can be turned into strings, `keyup` seems to work:\n\n``` js\ndocument.addEventListener('keyup', \n  function(e) { console.log('keyup capture', e); }, \n  true /* grab event on tunnel, not on bubble */);\n```\n"
